Package de.modlab.smilib.io

Interface Summary
SmilesReader<E extends Fragment> Interface used by all SmilesReaders.
SmilesWriter Interface used by all SmiLib SmilesWriters.
 

Class Summary
ConformityChecker Checks whether source SMILES are SmiLib conform.
Preprocessor Preprocesses SMILES so that they can be used by SmiLib.
SmilesFileReader<E extends Fragment> Reads SMILES from the input files.
SmilesFileWriter Writes SMILES in a file.
SmilesGuiReader Parses SMILES to molecule fragments when SMILES are entered in the GUI mask.
SmilesGuiWriter Writes SMILES to a JTextArea.
SmilesLineWriter Writes SMILES to the command line.
SmilesToSDFWriter Writes the molecules created as SMILES in a SD file.
